{"tid":231873,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[講出真相後果] 徐曉冬直播哭訴被除名 什剎海體校爆真相","createTime":"2017-05-06T11:02:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-06T13:30:56.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e18d0b23b4b6beac145b6ac10fafe2d958b6e950","tid":231873,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T11:02:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170506/56657536\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170506%2F56657536&d=zhjqHwqbwmwTWRz%2FWGYaULIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=71518fe6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170506%2F56657536&h=930fa864\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170506/56657536</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170506/large/1494042896_d38e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170506%2Flarge%2F1494042896_d38e.jpg&h=636d480b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「格鬥狂人」徐曉冬20秒擊倒太極宗師魏雷（雷雷）後，向武林各派發戰帖，還批評「中國傳統武術都是假的」。原本他還要赴台灣與近日爆紅的「館長」陳之漢交流，卻因故作罷，前日他在直播中哭訴自己遭污衊是「特務」事件，引發熱烈討論。<br />\n<br />\n徐曉冬在前日的直播中，哭訴自己被母校什剎海體校除名，還被要求刪除所有有關該校的貼文，他說「我是什剎海畢業的，在什剎海待了10多年。我一個人推廣MMA（綜合格鬥），全中國沒有人知道MMA，我的腿受傷了，武協管過我嗎？你國家體育局管過我嗎？」「我代表中國人打比賽，現在很多中國人來罵我！」「我一個人辦比賽，一個人蹭錢，一個人投錢，就是想給有夢想的中國年輕人一個機會，我為中國人做事，我哪裏賣國了？」他更哭說：「我去趟美國就成特務了？我去趟台灣就成特務了？我接受台灣2間電視台的採訪，我就成特務了？」<br />\n<br />\n雖然徐曉冬在直播中痛哭流涕，抱怨自己被北京市什剎海體校除名，但該校透露，上世紀90年代徐曉冬只在什剎海培訓中心培訓過2年，但這種培訓只需自己花錢，不會通過考試，並非其正式學員。徐也一直沒有進入體校的專業隊，更不是學校的教練員。此外，有內地媒體記者到其經營的「必圖拳館」查訪，發現徐在簡介中自稱「國家一級運動員」，但相關人士指，通過散打獲得國家一級運動員的機會比較少。簡介中又指他是「國家特級教練員」，但武協相關人員稱「從來沒有這個職稱」。<br />\n<br />\n綜合報道"},{"pid":"11ecf1710803c5fe752fe8e20f011fc3d7e5ad2a","tid":231873,"uid":7915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T11:26:50.000Z","msg":"遲啲直頭冇咗依個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56c102ec5d6a920f50112dd330f80164c749ede4","tid":231873,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T11:28:59.000Z","msg":"咪移民黎香港呀"},{"pid":"f0f365d168a0de034a2180f964a8d4454e40712f","tid":231873,"uid":86097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T11:29:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"383b437c96eb1da6825ea9d702b3b1a65386d176","tid":231873,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T11:29:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>遲啲直頭冇咗依個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢再玩大應該會俾人約傾計<br />\n從此自己消失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d374b2d485c3c29633ca97a054cf8577a698a0f","tid":231873,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T11:31:08.000Z","msg":"去美加囉"},{"pid":"1fba39ea94d62f69beed79b5ab4d742f6b7b1d44","tid":231873,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T11:32:31.000Z","msg":"係咪即係無人敢應戰 ?"},{"pid":"65ad366621e8c60ba62c47e9e4ea57528754c8e5","tid":231873,"uid":98653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T11:33:26.000Z","msg":"硬係覺得片尾爭緊一句大嗌&quot;食屎狗&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aead0f854cfab561cb4420c94e03138dcd632199","tid":231873,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T11:42:42.000Z","msg":"支持佢打柒班友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"998a94fed6718d4145a4b541f59081fbe1defc4b","tid":231873,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T11:46:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支持佢打柒班友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無人敢應戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nmma無名無姓既都尚且如此，<br />\n如果出mma個鬍鬚佬(唔記得咩名)仲無得打"},{"pid":"98e38